title: Eps. 116 - Second Hand Screaming
description:
On this week’s podcast the 3 Amigo’s are back together again and they’re talking about giving. Is it hard for you to give ? Do you believe that if you give it will be given back to you ? CJ poses the question to ET in regards to how it’s so easy for him to give without thinking twice about it. The answer to his question isn’t based on the amount of money in your bank account it’s a mindset and the guys are going to teach you how to get a giver’s mindset.
